      "translation": "(1') To ..., ..., king of Sumer and Akkad , dedicated this ( vessel ) for his well-being ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001008.4",
      "line_range": "4",
      "translation": "(4') Whoever erases this inscription and writes his own name there , may Nanna , my master , ( and ) my [ ... ] , Ningal ... that person !"
    }
